    • main

      public static void main(String[] args)
      Main for Implementor to launch implement(Class, Path) or implementJar(Class, Path). If count of arguments is one then launch implement(Class, Path). If count of arguments is three then launch implementJar(Class, Path).
      Parameters:
      args - : class name for implement(Class, Path) or class name and path to write jar for implementJar(Class, Path).
